text: There's a purity to what Nintendo did with these two games that can't and won't be replicated. You had an incredible preceding game that revolutionized the series by bringing it flawlessly into 3D for the first time, creating easily one of the greatest games of all time... and then you had an unlikely, brilliantly twisted mirror universe version of THAT classic that brought the series into the (uncharacteristically) darkest place Zelda has ever gone... and it all somehow worked!
